```

### STEP 5: INTEGRATE WITH CONTENT GENERATION

Update your content generation functions:

```javascript
// EXAMPLE: Text Generation
async function generateText(prompt) {
  if (userInfo.realCredits <= 0) {
    alert('Insufficient credits! Please top up your account.');
    return;
  }

  // Track usage before generation
  await trackUsage('Text Generation', 1, `Generated text for: "${prompt.substring(0, 30)}..."`);

  // Your existing text generation logic here
