## IMPLEMENTATION STEPS:

1. **Replace user authentication code** with the enhanced version
2. **Add credit sync functions** to communicate with main website
3. **Implement usage tracking** for all content generation
4. **Update UI components** to show real user data
5. **Add workspace isolation** for projects and transactions
6. **Test credit synchronization** between Penora and main website

## EXPECTED RESULTS:

‚úÖ Each user gets their own isolated workspace
‚úÖ Real credit tracking synced with main website  
‚úÖ Usage history shows actual user activities
‚úÖ Credits decrease as user generates content
‚úÖ No shared data between different users
‚úÖ Real-time sync with sukusuku.ai main website

## CRITICAL: TESTING CHECKLIST

1. User "Lucifer Jhon" sees only their own data
2. Credits reflect real usage (decreases with each generation)
3. Transaction history shows actual user activities
4. Workspace is completely isolated from other users
5. Credit sync works with main sukusuku.ai website
6. New users get clean, empty workspace

Apply this complete fix to resolve all workspace isolation and credit synchronization issues.

