2. Replace the current user handling code with the code above
3. Update all references to user data to use the `userInfo` state
4. Test by accessing ImageGene through sukusuku.ai
5. Check browser console for any error messages

This will properly decode the JWT token sent from sukusuku.ai and display the correct user information including name, email, and credit balance.

